8 An Act relating to schools; amending 70 O.S. 2021,
Section 13-116, which relates to use of corporal
9 punishment on certain students; prohibiting use of
corporal punishment on any student identified with
10 certain disability; removing language authorizing
certain waiver; providing an effective date; and
11 declaring an emergency.
12
13
14 BE IT ENACTED BY THE PEOPLE OF THE STATE OF OKLAHOMA:
15 SECTION 1. AMENDATORY 70 O.S. 2021, Section 13-116, is
16 amended to read as follows:
17 Section 13-116. A. School district personnel shall be
18 prohibited from using corporal punishment on students any student
19 identified with the most significant cognitive disabilities
20 according to criteria established by the State Department of
21 Education unless addressed in an annual individualized education
22 program (IEP) developed a disability in accordance with the
23 Individuals with Disabilities Education Act (IDEA).
24
